@startuml

hide footbox

title Diagrama de Sequência: Reserva de Instalação (RF-7.1)

autonumber

actor "Treinador" as Coach
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "API REST" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Coach -> UI: Solicita Reserva (recurso, horário)
activate UI

UI -> API: POST /api/v1/reservations
activate API

API -> DB: Verificar Conflitos (SQL Overlap)
activate DB
DB --> API: count (sobreposições)
deactivate DB

alt count > 0 (Conflito)
    API --> UI: HTTP 409 Conflict
    UI --> Coach: Exibe erro e sugestões
else count == 0 (Livre)
    API -> DB: INSERT INTO reservations (status='Confirmed')
    activate DB
    DB --> API: success
    deactivate DB
    API --> UI: HTTP 201 Created
    UI --> Coach: Confirmação de Reserva
end

deactivate API
deactivate UI

@enduml
